name: TurtSat
description: Turtsat is a community-driven open platform for ordinals, with a mission to become the Gitcoin of Ordinals, providing a space for everyone to buidl, donate, and impact Bitcoin Ordinals & BRC-20 through Turtsat. Our platform will feature a fundamental donation protocol, enabling more open-source developers and communities to participate in the ecological development of Ordinals and enjoy the benefits.
